Mahasiswa FABU jayakan Global Learning Expedition ke Indonesia
==============================================================

by [fadzly](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/author/fadzly/ "Posts by fadzly")
 | Dec 15, 2024 | [News](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/category/news/)

![](https://builtsurvey.utm.my/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-14-at-22.14.43-1024x576-1.jpeg)

**JAWA TENGAH, 25 Nov –** Seramai 31 orang mahasiswa Tahun 3 dan 4, Ijazah Sarjana Muda Perancangan Bandar dan Wilayah, Fakulti Alam Bina dan Ukur (FABU), Universiti Teknologi Malaysia (UTM) telah terlibat di dalam program ‘Global Learning Expedition 2.0: Exploring Rural Java through International Field Study and UTM-UNDIP-UNS Joint Student Rural Seminar’, yang berlangsung sepanjang tempoh cuti pertengahan semester bermula pada 24 hingga 30 November 2024. Berita lanjut di : [https://news.utm.my/ms/2024/11/mahasiswa-fabu-jayakan-global-learning-expedition-ke-indonesia/](https://news.utm.my/ms/2024/11/mahasiswa-fabu-jayakan-global-learning-expedition-ke-indonesia/)
